== Weaksauce ==


Weaksauce is a term commonly used amongst online gamers to describe someone as being weak or providing little challenge.  The term "weaksauce" was coined in Hawaii.  It was not a very widespread word, but it was used by some highschool students. It was the year 2000 when "weaksauce" was introduced to the online world.  The Hawaii counter-strike clan Liquor Shot, began using the term weaksauce online and it caught on very quickly throughout the entire CS community.  Specifically it was member .liqshot|King Midas. who introduced the word to everyone in the clan.  He had heard the word from his friends who attended Aiea High School.

There are also some other variations of this word that have popped up.  You may see people use words like: dopesauce, 1337sauce, and pwnsauce.There is also a Hawaii based "auto enthusiast" website called "Racesauce".